MasterCard,Retail,Locations,Insights,is,a,real,estate,solution,for,generating,performance,metrics,of,specified,merchant,retail,locations,The,integration,of,the,MasterCard,Retail,Locations,Insights,API,facilitates,access,to,monthly,updated,data,of,the,business,performance,of,individual,retail,locations,It,uses,a,scoring,system,to,show,the,growth,trends,market,stability,ratings,sales,and,transactions,volumes,and,ticket,sizes,of,the,specified,merchant,locations,The,API,is,a,useful,platform,for,evaluating,and,validating,the,viability,of,a,particular,business,location,in,terms,of,customer,traffic,rental,costs,and,growth,potential